D-clock measuring
D-clock master sporadic 0.0, 2.0, 4.0, 6.0
tag relation master = measuring
D-clock doreset sporadic 2.0, 5.5, 9.0
tag relation doreset = measuring
U-clock slave // no reset
master time delayed by 3.0 on measuring implies slave
U-clock slave_reset // default delayed weak reset
master time delayed by 3.0 on measuring with reset on doreset implies slave_reset

@policy asap
@step
@step
@step
@step
@step
@step
@print